Deemos got a fiendish idea, the Maximals, he never betrayed them, he moved =
into a base out in the woods, but he never actually "left" the Maximals. He=
 contacted Kluster on his commlink. (He was talking to Kluster before)

Dee=
mos: Sir Kluster, are you there? This is Deemos, of the Maximals. If you ar=
e hearing this, I have something to report. My sub-Maximal group has as of =
now, aligned with the Alliance. The Alliance are not bad at all, and would =
be delighted (Deemos doesn't know if they would be, he's just saying this) =
if you would align with them, too, it would help both factions greatly, and=
 the other minor groups will quickly be defeated if the 2 biggest and best =
factions in the Neo Beast Wars teamed up, please consider this, Sir Kluster=
. Deemos out...
